getMatchingAssistantsOnShiftBookableRooms() - Method in class BookingSystem
Creates assistant on shift and bookable room pairs in order to make bookings Does so by ensuring that both of them have the status that lets them be booked, while checking if their date matches If these conditions are satisfied then the assistant on shift is appended to an arraylist and the bookable room is appended to another They can then be retrieved by using the same index to retrieve both objects, since each pair will have the same index
